data.description: Cul-de-sac location opposite Embudo Hills Park with city and mountain views in desirable foothills neighborhood.  Open floor plan with large rooms.  Light and bright with lots of windows (some wood). New carpet and interior paint. Attractive tile floors. Active solar electric with solar panels installed in 2021.  Electric bills of only $8.17 per month.  Covered patio with open flagstone patio.  Large private back yard.  Quiet location. TPO roof = 2015. Custom house built by Pickard
